---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Learn More – Recovery Roads"
  description="Learn more about Recovery Roads – our mission, how it works, and how to find recovery resources."
>
  <section class="page-hero parallax" style="background-image: url('https://recoveryroads.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/asphalt-environment-grass-highway-239520.jpg')">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Learn More</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__sub">
        About Recovery Roads and our mission to share stories of experience, strength, and hope.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container about-content">
      <div class="about-content__section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Recovery Roads is dedicated to capturing and sharing unscripted recovery stories. We believe every person in recovery has a unique journey worth telling — and that sharing these stories builds a bridge of hope for those still struggling.
        </p>
        <p>
          We hit the open road, invite people into a relaxed, one-on-one conversation, and let the story unfold naturally. No scripts, no pressure — just fresh air, sunshine, and genuine dialogue.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-content__section">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <ol class="about-content__steps">
          <li>
            <strong>Reach Out</strong> — Fill out the form on our <a href="/share">Share Your Story</a> page. Let us know you're interested.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>We Connect</strong> — We'll reach out to schedule a time that works for you. We come to you, or meet somewhere scenic.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Hit the Road</strong> — We go for a drive, have a conversation, and capture your story in a relaxed, natural way.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Share &amp; Inspire</strong> — With your permission, we share your story to inspire others on their own recovery journey.
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="about-content__section about-content__resources">
        <h2>Recovery Resources</h2>
        <p>
          Looking for recovery support? Visit our partner site for resources:
        </p>
        <a href="https://nextstepky.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">
          Visit Next Step &#8599;
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="about-content__section about-content__memorial">
        <p>
          <strong>Recovery Roads is dedicated in loving memory of Jesse Allen Roth &amp; Stephanie Suzanne Crawford.</strong>
          Their stories live on through every person we reach.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8rem 1.5rem 5rem;
    min-height: 350px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .page-hero__sub {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content__section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-content__section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
  }

  .about-content__section p {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-content__steps {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-content__steps li {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-left: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-content__steps li strong {
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .about-content__resources {
    background: #f5f5f5;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-content__resources p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content__memorial {
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-content__memorial p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>
